            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Apollini et Hygiae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ulp</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Felix <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipii</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Brig</abbr><ex>etionis</ex></expan> porticum <lb n="4"/>a portis II ad fon<lb break="no" n="5"/>tem Salutis a <lb n="6"/>solo inpendi<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <lb n="7"/>suis fecit et <lb n="8"/>ad epulas <expan><abbr>privileg</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>colleg</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>centon</abbr><ex>ariorum</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>haberi iussit <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sab</abbr><ex>ino</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>q<expan><ex>uin</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>uennale</ex></expan> Pr<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>esente</abbr></expan> et <expan><abbr>Extric</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Noni</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>No</abbr><ex>vembribus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Inschriftfeld mit gewelltem Rahmen, sog. &amp;apos;Barockmotiv&amp;apos;. Z. 1: ET-, AE-Ligaturen; Z.2: LP-, AV-Ligaturen; Z. 6: ND-Ligatur; Z. 10: NI-Ligatur; Lesung unsicher, möglicherweise auch &amp;apos;No(nis) Iun(iis)&amp;apos;. Eine weitere Bauinschrift des selben Stifters für einen Tempel an Apollo und Hygia: http://edh-www.adw.uni-heidelberg.de/edh/inschrift/HD038313 sowie für eine schola: http://edh-www.adw.uni-heidelberg.de/edh/inschrift/HD039386.</p>
            </div>
